00:34:46.171 --> 00:34:47.920
have to say about
artificial intelligence?

00:34:47.920 --> 00:34:49.380
N. T. WRIGHT: Yeah,
that's a great question,

00:34:49.380 --> 00:34:51.171
and I'd like to know
