wisdom to know what

00:37:14.190 --> 00:37:17.730
to do with the possibilities
that we have in front

00:37:17.730 --> 00:37:20.695
of us-- that's the difference
between information and wisdom,

00:37:20.695 --> 00:37:21.195
I think.

