which is super efficient,

00:39:18.240 --> 00:39:20.770
but which actually squelches
genuine humanness over

00:39:20.770 --> 00:39:23.070
on one side and does
not produce anything

00:39:23.070 --> 00:39:25.340
other than brutalist
boxes on the other.

00:39:25.340 --> 00:39:27.190
